  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. Applying the distributive property on the left- and right-hand sides of the given equation yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x squared, plus 2 x, plus 3 x, plus 6, equals, x squared, minus 2 x, minus 3 x, plus 6, plus 10\"></span>, or <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x squared, plus 5 x, plus 6, equals, x squared, minus 5 x, plus 16\"></span>. Subtracting <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x squared \"></span> from and adding <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"5 x\"></span> to both sides of this equation yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"10 x plus 6, equals 16\"></span>. Subtracting 6 from both sides of this equation and then dividing both sides by 10 yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x equals 1\"></span>.<p>Choices B, C, and D are incorrect. Substituting 0, <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"negative 2\"></span>, or <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"negative 5\"></span> for <span class=\"italic\">x</span> in the given equation will result in a false statement. If <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x equals 0\"></span>, the given equation becomes <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"6 equals 16\"></span>; if <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x equals negative 2\"></span>, the given equation becomes <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"0 equals 30\"></span>; and if <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x equals negative 5\"></span>, the given equation becomes <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"6 equals 66\"></span>. Therefore, the values 0, <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"negative 2\"></span>, and <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"negative 5\"></span> aren&rsquo;t solutions to the given equation.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p>\n",
